T1  - Aspiration Performance and Railroads’ Patterns of Learning from Train Wrecks and Crashes
AU  - Baum, Joel A. C.
AU  - Dahlin, Kristina B.
Y1  - 2007/06/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/orsc.1060.0239
